sub_title: Postdoc at Swammerdam Institute for Life Sciences (SILS), University of Amsterdam
summary:
I’m a researcher with proficient experience in structural biology/X-ray crystallography, structure-based drug design and profound knowledge in protein biochemistry, expression, refolding and purification.  
I am curious to discover mechanisms underlying metabolic processes and the development of disease; currently expanding my knowledge in the field of plant-pathogen interactions.
